				<div class=3D"elementor-widget-container">
					<p>WalletHub=E2=80=99s analysts calculated the potential monetary loss=
es =E2=80=94 including the cumulative cost of a cigarette pack per day over=
 several decades, health care expenditures, income losses and other costs =
=E2=80=94 brought on by smoking and exposure to secondhand smoke.</p>
<p>WalletHub estimated the financial cost of smoking in the U.S. to be roug=
hly <strong>$1.6 million per smoker over a lifetime</strong>.</p>
